title: Gluten Free Pumpkin Pie | Thanksgiving Recipe | Jon Rotherham
description:
It's nearly Thanksgiving FoodTubers! So Jon Rotherham, head chef at Jamie’s Fifteen restaurant, has a beautiful pumpkin pie recipe for the holidays. Roasted pumpkins, cinnamon, nutmeg and vanilla create a sweet and festive flavoured filling nestled inside a buttery, crisp gluten free pastry case. Absolutely delicious for everyone!

Full recipe: http://goo.gl/jnz7O6

Jamieoliver.com has loads more gluten free, vegetarian, vegan, and dairy free recipes right here : http://goo.gl/lKOUzL And plenty of traditional Thanksgiving recipes too: http://goo.gl/h8LVbX  Happy Holidays!

And if you’ve got a taste for pumpkin why not make a Vegan Pumpkin Pie Smoothie? Check out the recipe over on Drinks Tube: http://goo.gl/hS6YCS
